{"tid":2110802,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"港台停售節目予蘋果","createTime":"2020-07-16T06:57:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-16T08:07:23.000Z","uid":25558,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"65fd94e19ea8ff03cf6420b58409e7747c46f67f","tid":2110802,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T06:57:21.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200716/NYY4AWLXKCQM37Y2FIL32RGGMU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200716%2FNYY4AWLXKCQM37Y2FIL32RGGMU%2F&d=CgM6%2BPDcwTI4Uk%2BisK9n3%2F3ZlJXgeXtiTXALECG4O5Q%3D&h=02a78bdc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200716%2FNYY4AWLXKCQM37Y2FIL32RGGMU%2F&h=3db5eb4b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200716/NYY4AWLXKCQM37Y2FIL32RGGMU/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n港台停售節目予蘋果<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/P8x4o4N2id7SVDV7S-e9kwTwoZc=/585x428/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/OG7X43TQETIEE5F22SYABT6KV4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FP8x4o4N2id7SVDV7S-e9kwTwoZc%3D%2F585x428%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FOG7X43TQETIEE5F22SYABT6KV4.jpg&h=4e2e198b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n《鏗鏘集》每逢周二於本報「果燃台」的平台上架。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】資訊自由已經成。。。。。。。。。。。。。。即大概8月中後，《鏗鏘集》的往後集數將不能於「果燃台」播放。<br />\n<br />\n自今年3月初起，本報向港台洽購，以預付方式買入《鏗鏘集》版權，每十集為一個合約。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n稱欲集中點擊率<br />\n<br />\n惟港台機構傳訊總監伍曼儀。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n立法會議員毛孟靜表示，早前有建制派議員於立法會上點名批評港台節目於《蘋果》網上平台播放，相信港台因此承受一定政治壓力，「時機上太巧合」。港台節目即使在《蘋果》播放，根本難以說成是幫其製作節目，而港台向本報出售節目版權，亦可獲得版權費，幫補節目製作費。如需計算節目點擊率，也可以向本報查詢，一同計入總點擊率，港台決定令人感遺憾。"},{"pid":"cf9b6a882a8466cf76867019396c8cc0622d4e0c","tid":2110802,"uid":28195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"65fd94e19ea8ff03cf6420b58409e7747c46f67f","tid":2110802,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T06:57:21.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200716/NYY4AWLXKCQM37Y2FIL32RGGMU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200716%2FNYY4AWLXKCQM37Y2FIL32RGGMU%2F&d=CgM6%2BPDcwTI4Uk%2BisK9n3%2F3ZlJXgeXtiTXALECG4O5Q%3D&h=02a78bdc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200716%2FNYY4AWLXKCQM37Y2FIL32RGGMU%2F&h=3db5eb4b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200716/NYY4AWLXKCQM37Y2FIL32RGGMU/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n港台停售節目予蘋果<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/P8x4o4N2id7SVDV7S-e9kwTwoZc=/585x428/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/OG7X43TQETIEE5F22SYABT6KV4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FP8x4o4N2id7SVDV7S-e9kwTwoZc%3D%2F585x428%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FOG7X43TQETIEE5F22SYABT6KV4.jpg&h=4e2e198b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n《鏗鏘集》每逢周二於本報「果燃台」的平台上架。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】資訊自由已經成。。。。。。。。。。。。。。即大概8月中後，《鏗鏘集》的往後集數將不能於「果燃台」播放。<br />\n<br />\n自今年3月初起，本報向港台洽購，以預付方式買入《鏗鏘集》版權，每十集為一個合約。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n稱欲集中點擊率<br />\n<br />\n惟港台機構傳訊總監伍曼儀。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n立法會議員毛孟靜表示，早前有建制派議員於立法會上點名批評港台節目於《蘋果》網上平台播放，相信港台因此承受一定政治壓力，「時機上太巧合」。港台節目即使在《蘋果》播放，根本難以說成是幫其製作節目，而港台向本報出售節目版權，亦可獲得版權費，幫補節目製作費。如需計算節目點擊率，也可以向本報查詢，一同計入總點擊率，港台決定令人感遺憾。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T07:01:35.000Z","msg":"其實有幾多人會經蘋果睇港台節目？<br />\n蘋果手動出link仲好，又唔洗俾錢港台。"},{"pid":"60c390b01ae0fa95bae2d983a7c83f2ecb94b1cb","tid":2110802,"uid":10540,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T07:04:27.000Z","msg":"其實點解公共廣播都要俾錢買版權？<br />\n人哋外國已經用Public Domain。"},{"pid":"c0fcfd467e66502eb87b96a81deacd5